    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893800/extras/cd66bf7e2951e43cb574733157c1c91e.avif?t=1762152199\" width=639 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scuffy Game is a First-Person Multiplayer fan made scuffed version of any party games that let's you play various minigames to play with friends (or by yourself. Your choice). Play different minigames and let one minigame decide who's the last one standing to and win it all. <strong>(Totally not trying to reference a game that copied a TV show from a couple of months ago)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Base Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 20 players </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 Maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Game Modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Server List</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bugs (LOTS OF BUGS... maybe)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your still not satisficed with the game, just listen to what some of our costumers have to say!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893800/extras/1aebc151a6353c2d9ec3c7868e3645f5.avif?t=1762152199\" width=100 height=100 /></span> What type of game is this? I give this game a 1/10. - Guy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Picture of Guy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893800/extras/1aebc151a6353c2d9ec3c7868e3645f5.avif?t=1762152199\" width=100 height=100 /></span> I... I mean... this game is good. It's really fun to... play with friends and family. - Also Guy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Picture of Guy</p>",
